    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine currently struggles to start and has a significant oil leak, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. The interior has sustained significant wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It will require a trailer for transport and substantial mechanical work to be roadworthy again.",
